description:
Add support for user-created channels beyond agent channels.

## Features
- Create public channels (visible to all workspace members)
- Create private channels (invite-only)
- Channel descriptions and topics
- Pin messages in channels
- Channel member list
- Leave/archive channels

## Data Model
```typescript
interface Channel {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  description?: string;
  topic?: string;
  isPrivate: boolean;
  workspaceId: string;
  createdBy: string;
  members: string[];
  pinnedMessages: string[];
  createdAt: Date;
}
```

## API Endpoints
- POST /api/channels - Create channel
- GET /api/channels - List workspace channels
- PATCH /api/channels/:id - Update channel
- DELETE /api/channels/:id - Archive channel
- POST /api/channels/:id/members - Add member
- DELETE /api/channels/:id/members/:userId - Remove member

Add emoji reactions to messages.

## Features
- React with any emoji
- See who reacted
- Reaction counts
- Custom workspace emojis
- Keyboard shortcut to react

## Data Model
```typescript
interface Reaction {
  messageId: string;
  emoji: string;
  userId: string;
  createdAt: Date;
}
```
